  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sight to Bright - Restore Sight for Education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will vision screen all the school children in Vavuniya District of Sri Lanka and will provide free custom made spectacles for students who are suffering from refractive errors. Students who are suffering from other vision problems will be referred to the regional eye surgeons and necessary steps will be taken to support their continuity of Care. THe project will be the first of it kind to serve communities of Vavuniya who are still recovering from the civil conflict ended in 2009.</narrative>
  </description>
